==Description==

The [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignCenter.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet AlignCenter''' tool aligns the contents of selected cells to the center horizontally.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select one or more cells.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignCenter.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignCenter|Align center]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Alignment → [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignCenter.svg|16px]] Align center}} option from the menu.


